Na fana usang'hano uwo woukalile wokutenda munhu yadanganike wandikigwe muna yamabwe wiza muna utunhizo uwo, wanhu wa Isilaeli hawadahile bule kulola kuna ichitala cha Musa kwa ichimu cha utunhizo uwo, hata fana utunhizo uja ukala uhowa,
Weye vino, vino usang'hano wa Muhe wa Mulungu hauzakuwa na utunhizo mkulu ng'hani bule?
Na one usang'hano woukalile wokwing'ha wanhu nhaguso ukala na utunhizo, vino usang'hano woukalile wokwing'ha wanhu unovu hauzakuwa na utunhizo mkulu ng'hani!
Kwaviya chinhu chiya chikalile na utunhizo siku zino hachina utunhizo fana vichilinganyize na utunhizo uno wa lagano da sambi.
Fana chinhu chiya chidanganike chizile muna utunhizo, vino hachizakuwa na utunhizo mkulu ng'hani kwa chinhu chiya chochigendelela!
